{"tid":1370712,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登」新意義：「連成一線 各自攀登」","createTime":"2019-07-27T05:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:01:27.000Z","uid":101392,"like":81,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e6698eafe45d2aaca7ab49cc967e6d7a6c21443","tid":1370712,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"「連登」<br />\n「連」連成一線 大家都係兄弟<br />\n「登」各自攀登 各自爬山<br />\n<br />\n「連」：創辦人「連尼住 」<br />\n「登」：除咗係脫胎自高登，亦都可以解「登高望遠」，象徵創辦人「望遠」<br />\n<br />\n今次泛民、本土、港獨、和理非、勇武、甚至社會各界、AO、EO、淺黃淺藍<br />\n全部都「連」成一線 各自攀「登」<br />\n正正係兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n各有各做之餘<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰不指責不分化"},{"pid":"0f8c7881d58f273d5bdf6e08b0624cba176d3730","tid":1370712,"uid":278886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:31:40.000Z","msg":"不割 不分!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815e61801a75dc6744881c3610aa473b93a0cf81","tid":1370712,"uid":64193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼"},{"pid":"40c96d883aa55c83e4968b414e55a8f9912fc98d","tid":1370712,"uid":70973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連成一線 各自攀登</span>"},{"pid":"c607274440f64f63dbaffaf1c36c3b7c018fc38b","tid":1370712,"uid":158499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"連結人民，齊上齊落齊攀登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb1881057bd2f49c75cf2661676b8cdf51d97dd","tid":1370712,"uid":39838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"815e61801a75dc6744881c3610aa473b93a0cf81","tid":1370712,"uid":64193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"他朝香港獨立<br />\n我絕對支持用獅子山下做國歌<br />\n每次香港有難<br />\n香港人都會發揮獅子山精神互愛互助<br />\n